  "3211990": {
    "name": "Arcas Champions: Gorilla Warfare",
    "steam_appid": 3211990,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Arcas Champions</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211990/extras/dcd7803e1cd0797d37df8ce6da895832.avif?t=1763562556\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211990/extras_big/dcd7803e1cd0797d37df8ce6da895832.avif?t=1763562556 width=800 height=170 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到 Arcas Champions，一款充满激情的第三人称能力射击游戏，背景设定在猿类母星的核心区域。在这里，派系冲突、奇异地貌和强大技能交织，每场战斗都令人热血沸腾。选择你的冠军，掌握独特能力，在这片神秘且茂密的世界中奋战，争夺主导地位。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏背景</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211990/extras/8a0d902efb00698322dbd5bbd14a3204.avif?t=1763562556\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211990/extras_big/8a0d902efb00698322dbd5bbd14a3204.avif?t=1763562556 width=800 height=170 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arcas 世界正陷入内战。一艘外星飞船的突然坠毁，导致人们重新发现了 Bastonium——一种神秘而强大的远古元素，蕴藏着无限潜力，同时也极具危险性。这一发现点燃了战火，叛军游击队与村庄精英传统主义者为争夺星球的控制权展开激战。随着双方势力争夺 Bastonium 的力量，自然与科技的界限逐渐模糊，一场残酷的霸权之争即将爆发。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏玩法</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211990/extras/d97c0c2213b531f31759fb378a962573.avif?t=1763562556\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211990/extras_big/d97c0c2213b531f31759fb378a962573.avif?t=1763562556 width=800 height=170 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏围绕精心设计的冠军角色展开，每位冠军都拥有独特的属性、图腾能力和可定制的武器。你可以根据自己的游戏风格调整角色，无论是敏捷型、输出型还是支援型，都能找到适合的玩法。利用墙壁跳跃、滑翔和强力跃动，在激烈的丛林战斗中翻越障碍、迅速出击，并巧妙躲避敌人。只有高超的战术与精准的操作，才能在这片蛮荒世界中生存并称霸战场。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏模式</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211990/extras/8e3faaa09e59393a341493a26747f377.avif?t=1763562556\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211990/extras_big/8e3faaa09e59393a341493a26747f377.avif?t=1763562556 width=800 height=170 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在抢先体验阶段，玩家可以体验紧张刺激的在线团队对战模式，这些模式不仅需要策略，还考验反应速度。“部落战争”（TDM）、“部落霸权”（控制模式）、“斗殴”（淘汰模式）和“香蕉狂热”（提取模式）将率先上线，未来还会陆续推出更多模式。参与排位赛，提升排行榜排名，赢取声望和荣誉。随着段位的提升，你将在 Arcas 世界中获得更大的影响力，成为传奇般的存在。。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>议会</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211990/extras/9af43805558e9da994f81a5812ba507f.avif?t=1763562556\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211990/extras_big/9af43805558e9da994f81a5812ba507f.avif?t=1763562556 width=800 height=170 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arcas Champions 独特的“议会”功能，让高排名玩家能够影响游戏的未来。获得声望的冠军可以参与投票，决定关键更新，包括武器平衡调整、新游戏模式的加入，以及社区驱动的功能提案。你的意见将直接塑造 Arcas Champions 的发展，使其不仅仅是一款游戏，更是一个由玩家共建的世界，在这里，你的声音真正具有影响力。</p>",
